pillow>=11.0.0
# Chat audio (cloud STT/TTS + transcribe). Editable local package — its lean core
# deps (deepgram-sdk / cartesia / numpy / httpx / …) are pinned transitively below
# by `uv pip compile`. NOT the [localmodels] extra:
# the proxy uses cloud providers, so it skips the phone's on-box ONNX/transformers.
# Compile + install run from the repo root so `./audio` resolves consistently
# (dev `oto-dock/`, Docker `/app`, bare-metal `/opt/otodock`).
-e ./audio
